{"tid":968061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為用iPhone 發Twitter　陸媒引內部文件：涉事員工罰減薪五千　涉VPN問題","createTime":"2019-01-04T02:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T03:21:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"89d64e557b5461dded31e0399ee7fd26af798691","tid":968061,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/hua-01_O05up_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhua-01_O05up_1200x0.png&h=b22dc6fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為在大除夕（31日）於Twitter上發表新年祝福，但帖文卻顯示是由蘋果iPhone發出，引發公關災難。今日一張華為內部的問責文件在網上流出，涉事員工及主管分別被罰減薪五千元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n華為科技的官方Twitter在12月31日發表新年祝福，不過帖文下方卻顯示「via Twitter for iPhone」的字眼。華為隨即刪除帖文，但依然無法避免公關災難，引來全球各地媒體報道。<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體今日就發布一份，聲稱是在網上流出的華為問責決定文件。文件稱，該貼文發佈後，截圖出現在了部分海外和國內社交媒體上並廣泛傳播，該事件對華為手機的品牌帶來了不良影響。<br />\n<br />\n該內部文件指，事發當日因為VPN網絡問題，無法用電腦正常發帖，因此改用插入香港電話卡的iPhone手機發文，終導致今次的出錯。<br />\n<br />\n華為決定對直接責任人予以通報批評，個人職級降1級，月薪下調5000元人民幣。對數位行銷團隊主管予以通報批評，個人職級降級1級，月薪降5000元，並凍結個人職級晉升、漲薪，凍結期12個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/華為用iphone-發twitter-陸媒引內部文件-涉事員工罰減薪五千-涉vpn問題/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%94%A8iphone-%E7%99%BCtwitter-%E9%99%B8%E5%AA%92%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-%E6%B6%89%E4%BA%8B%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%BD%B0%E6%B8%9B%E8%96%AA%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%83-%E6%B6%89vpn%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%2F&d=pUPQkf61XcQGZPwxH5otP7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b78caa37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E7%94%A8iphone-%E7%99%BCtwitter-%E9%99%B8%E5%AA%92%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-%E6%B6%89%E4%BA%8B%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E7%BD%B0%E6%B8%9B%E8%96%AA%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%83-%E6%B6%89vpn%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%2F&h=385dd41c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/華為用iphone-發twitter-陸媒引內部文件-涉事員工罰減薪五千-涉vpn問題/</a>"},{"pid":"84489e173b2c058c2d56f39a8d948205f2ae3990","tid":968061,"uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T02:43:44.000Z","msg":"應該罰GFW嘛，係GFW阻住上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53e8a45148590339c1b831455767ec86bd4da1e","tid":968061,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T02:47:17.000Z","msg":"VPN<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4befa074268c487f220da5df75a718aa022f9826","tid":968061,"uid":105790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T02:48:12.000Z","msg":"vpn ?"},{"pid":"f97e2577cd03dc9d6904073535eaf3fc684fabeb","tid":968061,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T02:50:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"942d430bfefdcff180088a98aaa7cfba4d6ff0cc","tid":968061,"uid":182499,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"咁大間公司都要翻牆重要講出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29dee6b21ba0296d0463504d1f2ddcc10d09e9ec","tid":968061,"uid":35656,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T02:56:09.000Z","msg":"翻唔到牆改插香港電話卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f88cb32126c6b449bd5cb74c22e0f54fac2741","tid":968061,"uid":115525,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"柒完一獲再大大聲同全世界講自己要翻牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af746bf7e863f68a780769aa791d32fe69b304e7","tid":968061,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:00:39.000Z","msg":"大大聲講翻牆，本身合法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 